I think it sounds like he's trying to convey what it feels like to stumble through life while others around you seem to be moving on to bigger and better things. It can be depressing and discouraging and can make you feel like a failure, but if all you ever do is compare yourself to others you will never truly be happy. He even "stumbles" through the song, taking twice as long as normal to get the lyrics out. He's delayed, literally and figuratively.
